query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS algorithm_effect_records (
  id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  userId INT NOT NULL,
  accountId INT NOT NULL,
  targetId INT NOT NULL,
  targetType VARCHAR(20) NOT NULL,
  algorithmUsed VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
  previousBid DECIMAL(10, 2) NOT NULL,
  newBid DECIMAL(10, 2) NOT NULL,
  bidChangePercent DECIMAL(10, 2) NOT NULL,
  previousROAS DECIMAL(10, 2),
  previousACoS DECIMAL(10, 2),
  optimizationDate DATETIME NOT NULL,
  postROAS DECIMAL(10, 2),
  postACoS DECIMAL(10, 2),
  roasChange DECIMAL(10, 2),
  acosChange DECIMAL(10, 2),
  effectScore DECIMAL(10, 2),
  effectCalculatedAt DATETIME,
  confidenceScore DECIMAL(10, 2),
  holidayName VARCHAR(100),
  reason TEXT,
  createdAt DATETIME DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  INDEX idx_algorithm_effect_userId (userId),
  INDEX idx_algorithm_effect_accountId (accountId),
  INDEX idx_algorithm_effect_targetId (targetId),
  INDEX idx_algorithm_effect_algorithmUsed (algorithmUsed),
  INDEX idx_algorithm_effect_optimizationDate (optimizationDate)
);
